            <title>[SOLR-4985] solrconfig for hdfs example has wrong lucene match version in trunk</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-4985</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I see LUCENE_43 as the match version, but it should be LUCENE_50.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
