                            <comment id="13697527" author="rjernst" created="Tue, 2 Jul 2013 05:43:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ok this is confusing.  It looks like the solrconfig with the wrong version is under alt-configs/hdfs?  I had run ant example before, and then found solr/example/hdfs/collection1/conf/solrconfig.xml seems to get overwritten.  That seems wrong...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13697968" author="rjernst" created="Tue, 2 Jul 2013 16:55:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks like solr/example/hdfs isn&apos;t in source, and is instead populated by running &apos;ant example&apos;.  Not a clue why, but this patch fixes the lucene match version.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
